input: Subject: A charming seaside café; Characteristics: outdoor tables with white umbrellas; Timing and lighting: late afternoon with warm sunlight; Background: panoramic ocean view and boats on the horizon; Feeling: relaxed and inviting.
output: Capture a charming seaside café bathed in the warm glow of late afternoon sunlight.  Show rustic wooden tables adorned with crisp white umbrellas scattered across a patio overlooking a breathtaking vista. In the distance, sailboats dot the azure expanse of the ocean, creating a picturesque panorama against a vibrant sunset sky.  The scene should exude an atmosphere of relaxed serenity and unadulterated seaside charm, inviting viewers to linger and soak in the tranquility.
